title: Wasteland 2 Director's Cut (Patch 2.3.0.5) (GOG)
description:
Install instructions:
- Run "patch_wasteland2_directors_cut_2.3.0.5.exe"
- Play
PLEASE REMEMBER TO SEED, MANY OTHERS WANT THIS! :)
If you like this game, support the developers and BUY IT!

Change log:
This update adds mod support for Wasteland 2: Director's Cut.
This mod support update allows for users, among other things, to change and override template and prefab files used in the game
